title: UDPChat - Auto Update
description:
UDPChat is a direct connection UDP chat.
It is pretty useful in large buildings like work, school or other.
It has gotten different features like linking images, saving recent connections, popup window, and a Cheat Mode which makes the application 3% visible.
So far, you will be able to link images like .png, .jpg, .gif, .ico and .jpeg
All images and sessions will be saved (if you click yes to reconnect to user).
Note that this application ONLY works in local network LAN, but can be used over Hamachi

NOTE! This application might be recognized as a virus by antivirus softwares, it is not. And the reason for this is that the program contains adding itself to startup, which you can easily remove, by deleting the software itself
